                {
                    "id": "upstream_analytical_composed_solves",
                    "description": "Reproduces the upstream `Analytical: RadiationFundamentals composed system solves` test (test/radiation_fundamentals_test.jl:473-496). The upstream test compiles the composed system, solves it with the initial guess `radiation.energy_balance.T_e => 250.0`, and asserts `isapprox(sol[radiation.energy_balance.T_e], 255.0, rtol = 1.0e-2)` (Eq. 4.7, S&P p. 101). The migrated energy_balance subsystem uses the closed-form algebraic chain so no initial guess is needed; energy_balance.T_e is pinned both to the exact computed value 254.9909354243226 K (rel=1e-9) and to the upstream book value 255 K at the upstream rel=1.0e-2 bound.",
